<div class="container" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 120px auto 40px; padding: 0 20px;">
<h1 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 10px;">StockIQ Blog</h1>
<p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 40px;">Features, guides, and updates from the StockIQ team</p>

<!-- Blog Post: AI Stock Chat -->
<article class="blog-post" style="background: var(--card-bg); border-radius: 8px; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
<h2 style="color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 10px;">
<a href="#ai-chat" id="ai-chat" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: none;">Introducing AI Stock Chat - Your Personal Investment Assistant</a>
</h2>
<div style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">
<span>March 8, 2026</span> • <span>By Dave De Wit</span>
</div>
<div style="color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.6;">
<p>We're excited to announce our newest feature: <strong>AI Stock Chat</strong> - an intelligent assistant that helps you navigate StockIQ's powerful analysis tools and answers your investment questions in real-time.</p>

<h3 style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;">What Can AI Chat Do?</h3>
<ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
<li><strong>Direct Stock Analysis</strong> - Ask "Should I buy AAPL?" and get an instant clickable link to analyze Apple stock</li>
<li><strong>Feature Navigation</strong> - "How do I use the S&P 500 screener?" - AI guides you to the right tools</li>
<li><strong>Market Insights</strong> - Get quick answers about our 3,469 stock pages, crypto universe, and international screeners</li>
<li><strong>Personalized Help</strong> - AI knows if you're logged in and adjusts responses for your account status</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;">How to Use It</h3>
<p>Look for the blue chat button in the bottom-right corner of any page. Click it to start chatting! Your conversation history persists as you navigate between pages, so you can ask follow-up questions seamlessly.</p>

<h3 style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Smart & Context-Aware</h3>
<p>The AI knows about all StockIQ features including:</p>
<ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
<li>13 market screeners (S&P 500, NASDAQ 100, international markets)</li>
<li>Crypto universe analysis</li>
<li>Dashboard favorites and CSV exports</li>
<li>Pricing plans and free trial details</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Try It Now!</h3>
<p>The AI chat is live on all pages. Try asking questions like:</p>
<ul style="margin-left: 20px;">
<li>"Analyze TSLA"</li>
<li>"How does your crypto screener work?"</li>
<li>"Compare AAPL vs MSFT"</li>
<li>"What's included in the free trial?"</li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top: 25px;">We're continuously improving the AI's knowledge and capabilities. Have feedback? Let us know through the chat!</p>
</div>
</article>

